column5: And off ot LAKAIR......With a couple of stops on the way ,I should make it by 7ish.......See ya when you get there,or sorry for ones that can't make it......TC and very tight lines for all..............Chuck......
Tell em to post some pics. Safe drive and hope the weather and fishing is good.  Tight Lines  Nemo
Catch a biggun' for us losers stuck down here!
